definitions.definition: A European species of flatfish having dull brown colouring with reddish-brown blotches; fluke , European flounder ( Platichthys flesus ).
Any of various flatfish of the family Pleuronectidae or Bothidae .
A bootmaker 's tool for crimping boot fronts .
